title: Warpaint - Keep It Healthy - Disco-very (Remixes) (2014) FLAC
description:
El-P has remixed Warpaint's "Keep it Healthy", from their recent self-titled album. You can listen to it 
below. It's available digitally now, but will be released as a 12" in June with a Richard Norris Space + 
Time Machine remix of Warpaint's "Disco//very" on the B-side, via Rough Trade. (The digital release also
 features a Moody Good remix of "Disco//very".)
